!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
    %meta{:charset => "UTF-8"}/
    %title Lembrete
    %link{:href => "http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,300", :rel => "stylesheet", :type => "text/css"}/
    :css
      * {
          box-sizing: border-box;
          -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html,
      body {
          background: #eeeeee;
          font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif, Helvetica, Arial;
      }

      img {
          max-width: 100%;
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
          table tr td {
              width: 100% !important;
              float: left;
          }
      }
  %body{:style => "background: #eeeeee; padding: 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif, Helvetica, Arial;"}
    %center
      %table{:bgcolor => "FFFFFF", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :style => "background: #ffffff; max-width: 600px !important; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff;", :width => "100%"}
        %tr
          %td{:style => "padding: 20px; text-align: center; background: #4846b3;"}
            %h1{:style => "color: #ffffff"} Eventify
        %tr
          %td{:style => "padding: 20px; text-align: center;"}
            %p{:style => "font-size:20px; margin: 5px;"}
              Olá #{@user.email}
            %p
              Passando aqui para te lembrar do seu Evento "#{@event.title}"
              com data de início
              \#{I18n.l @event.starts_at, format: :short2}Hrs
              e data de fim #{I18n.l @event.ends_at, format: :short2}Hrs
        %tr
          %td{:style => "padding: 20px;"}
            %table{:border => "0", :cellpadding => "0"}
              %tr
                %td{:style => "width: 70%; padding: 10px; text-align: left;", :width => "70%"}
                  %h3 Descrição:
                  %p= @event.description
        %tr
          %td{:style => "padding: 20px; background: #2B2E34;"}
            %table{:a => "", :border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0"}
              %tr
                %td{:style => "width: 50%; padding: 10px; color: #ffffff; text-align: left;", :valign => "top", :width => "50%"}
                  %h2 Sobre nós
                  %p{:style => "font-size: 14px;"}
                    Aplicação para cadastrar Eventos onde o mesmo será possível
                    adicionar Lembretes a cada Evento, "lembrando que cada Evento terá no máximo 5
                    lembretes".
                %td{:style => "width: 50%; padding: 10px; color: #ffffff; text-align: left;", :valign => "top", :width => "50%"}
                  %h2 Contatos
                  %table{:border => "0", :style => "font-size: 14px;"}
                    %tr
                      %td Telefone: (88) 888-8888
                    %tr
                      %td Email: support@eventify.com
      %p{:style => "text-align: center; color: #666666; font-size: 12px; margin: 10px 0;"}
        Copyright © 2022. Todos os direitos reservados.
        %br/
